{"tid":918823,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"網友控：她爸害我家破人亡　MAMAMOO輝人認了「暗黑過往曝光」","createTime":"2018-11-27T13:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T17:06:26.000Z","uid":74065,"like":48,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"753315ab055067fd7f36c2b18e0eb73526516a4b","tid":918823,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"南韓女團MAMAMOO以驚人歌唱實力和舞台魅力闖出名聲，也即將成軍以來首次出席MAMA頒獎典禮。然而近來南韓演藝圈頻傳父母債務消息，這把火也燒到MAMAMOO成員輝人。27日南韓網路論壇出現爆料帖，稱自己因為輝人的父親家破人亡，經紀公司也對此做出回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3528/d3528964.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3528%2Fd3528964.jpg&h=1654dbd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MAMAMOO實力備受肯定。（圖／記者張一中攝）<br />\n<br />\n27日南韓各大網路論壇皆出現同一則爆料，以「因為MA女團成員的父親，我爸爸死了、家破人亡」為題，爆料網友稱自己的父親和該成員的父親做生意，原本不太信任對方，但這名成員的父親炫耀自己女兒是「MA女團」的成員，因為她很有名氣，「我們才相信對方」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3401/d3401314.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3401%2Fd3401314.jpg&h=9c773048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MAMAMOO近年來人氣超高。（圖／記者張一中攝）<br />\n<br />\n不過合作一段時間後，漸漸開始收不到貨款，一直追不到錢的情況下讓父親身心俱疲而病倒，最後被診斷胰腺癌，一直到死沒有收到該拿到的錢，更附上法院判決書照片證明所言不假。這則貼文立刻引起網友關注，被影射的MAMAMOO經紀公司，也承認對方所說的就是輝人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">隨後輝人也透過經紀公司也發出聲明，坦言該網友指稱的確實是自己的父親，但也吐露出辛酸：「我在沒有親生父親的照顧下長大，親生父親對家庭漠不關心，也是個失職的家長。成長過程中，我和家人常被意外的債務困擾，經常處於危險的狀態。」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3401/d3401311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3401%2Fd3401311.jpg&h=d4973e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MAMAMOO輝人（左）透過經紀公司承認，網友爆料的就是自己父親。（圖／記者張一中攝）<br />\n輝人也揭開瘡疤：「父母在2012年完婚，我的母親到幾個月前都還是信用不良的狀態。」更表示：「幾年前我最後一次和親生父親聯繫，拜託他不要讓我和母親受到更多傷害。之後他嘗試聯絡我幾次，我都沒有接受。這幾年來我們沒有交集、聯絡，甚至連他做什麼、住在哪裡都不知道。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3399/d3399756.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3399%2Fd3399756.jpg&h=8461c7f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MAMAMOO輝人在聲明中曝光關於親生父親的黑暗回憶。（圖／翻攝自tvN）<br />\n<br />\n輝人也承諾雖然聽到消息時也很震驚，但會努力和家人協商、解決問題，最後也對事件表達歉意，「對MAMAMOO成員們感到非常抱歉，最後，對於引起爭議，我也再次道歉。」<br />\n<br />\n垃圾老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n輝狗咁都中槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67576a01e2bccb73d2e7561705bb5a4505472a72","tid":918823,"uid":38904,"like":31,"dislike":90,"score":-59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"噉嘅樣都出道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其求一件 mk 妹都靚過佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce743746640d4e351ca2f176f069e371acea3554","tid":918823,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5619ed0d7c438d051044b525adb31e2441b877e2","tid":918823,"uid":52073,"like":55,"dislike":5,"score":50,"quote":{"pid":"67576a01e2bccb73d2e7561705bb5a4505472a72","tid":918823,"uid":38904,"like":31,"dislike":90,"score":-59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"噉嘅樣都出道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其求一件 mk 妹都靚過佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\